name: Ace
description:
These merged checkpoints aim to bring a more enhanced anime aesthetic while retaining the signature Anything style.

Please see "About this Version" for more information.

Ace V1 (release planned soon, just have to make the version page) is aimed to be a simple change from Anything (think of this as similar aesthetic but different details, without too much difference. A slight "spice up" if you will, nothing fancy).

Ace S is aimed to be a more styled/textured version of Ace (V1), retaining its compositions and slight detail changes while giving it a more painted/drawn sketch aesthetic.

modelVersions.name: S
modelVersions.description:
Example images for Ace S use the Real-ESRGAN X4+ Anime upscaler and Clip Skip 2 (these are just personal preference, though. Use whichever files and settings you desire).

Models mixed (and weighting):

Ace V1 (1).

PastelMix (.5): Pastel-Mix [Stylized Anime Model] - Fantasy.ai | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai

Yohan (-.5): andite/yohan-diffusion · Hugging Face (Yohan isn't on CivitAI right now, so here's the HuggingFace instead).

VAE used: NAI VAE/Anything (https://huggingface.co/andite/anything-v4.0/blob/main/anything-v4.0.vae.pt).
